  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><div style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:distribute-all-lines\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Straw\" title=\"House Straw\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"44\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/60px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/80px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/40px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/60px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/80px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\"><img alt=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Warrior%27s_Sons.svg/40px-Warrior%27s_Sons.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"44\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Warrior%27s_Sons.svg/60px-Warrior%27s_Sons.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/54/Warrior%27s_Sons.svg/80px-Warrior%27s_Sons.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <span style=\"display:inline-block;width:100%;text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Casper Straw</span></div></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></li><li>Captain of the <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a></li><li>Steward of the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Lickspittle\" title=\"High Lickspittle\">High Septon</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Straw\" title=\"House Straw\">House Straw</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_and_Blood\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fire and Blood\">Fire and Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Casper Straw</b> was a former <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Straw\" title=\"House Straw\">House Straw</a> who served the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Casper_Straw&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Casper was once a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> who served as a captain in the <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a>. After their abolition in the aftermath of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a>, Straw served as steward to the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Lickspittle\" title=\"High Lickspittle\">High Septon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/50_AC\" title=\"50 AC\">50&#160;AC</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Orryn_Baratheon\" title=\"Orryn Baratheon\">Orryn Baratheon</a> and a dozen <a href=\"/index.php/Men-at-arms\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Men-at-arms\">men-at-arms</a> came to the <a href=\"/index.php/Motherhouse\" title=\"Motherhouse\">motherhouse</a> attached to the <a href=\"/index.php/Starry_Sept\" title=\"Starry Sept\">Starry Sept</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>. On orders from his brother Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a>, Orryn demanded that Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaella_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aegon)\" title=\"Rhaella Targaryen (daughter of Aegon)\">Rhaella Targaryen</a>, a novice of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Faith\">Faith</a>, be given into his custody. The suspicious <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">Septa</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Karolyn\" title=\"Karolyn\">Karolyn</a>, under the guise of summoning the girl, instead sent for the High Septon. The <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlanders</a> were soon opposed by the alert and wary Casper and thirty armed <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septons</a>, who falsely claimed that forty <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">Hightower</a> knights were on their way, upon which Orryn and his men surrender and were taken into custody.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Casper_Straw&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, A Surfeit of Rulers.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404193931\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.085 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.295 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 632/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10523/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6247/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 786/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1223/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  279.539      1 -total\n 93.73%  262.014      1 Template:Infobox_cha